    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and minor dings, and the interior upholstery shows significant wear and some staining from regular use. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will likely require some routine maintenance in the near future, such as new tires and a brake service, to remain in peak operating condition. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle at an affordable price who doesn't mind some cosmetic imperfections.",
