    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a solid project or a functional daily driver. The exterior shows clear signs of its age, including several noticeable door dings, some paint fading on the hood and roof, and a few scuffs on the rear bumper. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but it will likely need some routine maintenance and suspension work in the near future to bring it back to peak performance. It\u2019s an honest car that needs a little TLC but offers a great foundation for the right owner.",
      "price": 22500.0,
