      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in great shape, runs super smoothly, and has been really well-loved. It\u2019s perfect for someone looking for a reliable car that still looks sharp on the road. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home\u2014come take it for a test drive and see for yourself!",
