    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for exceptional throttle response. The chassis maintains high torsional rigidity, supported by a refreshed suspension with poly-bushes and Bilstein dampers. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock. Crucial preventative maintenance has been executed, including subframe reinforcement and a VANOS overhaul. While exhibiting minor cosmetic patina consistent with spirited use, the mechanical vitals are synchronized and track-ready.",
      "price": 32500.0,
